      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e79f2d3af50ecdb44962b432efb39ea7d7d85931.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=2f77f6f4283e742f79e043f8a62274ec"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4c63d159ababeb885a3d5fff57b0c15ba51e03f0.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=a6ada30d996e978a592543af44bf16a8"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;The Ultimate Programming Bundle&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the world of programming with Packt’s Ultimate Programming Languages Bundle. Whether you’re writing your very first line of code or levelling up your professional skills, this collection of 35 expert books will guide you through today’s most important languages. Start at the foundation with accessible guides to Python and JavaScript, perfect for beginners who want to grasp the essentials quickly. Move up a tier to expand your toolkit with Java, C++, and Go, plus deeper dives into object-oriented programming and clean software design. Pay a little more and gain full access to the complete library of 26 additional titles, covering Rust, Kotlin, Swift, TypeScript, PHP, and Haskell alongside advanced Python, C++, and Java resources. Explore cookbooks, design pattern handbooks, and in-depth problem solvers that help you write cleaner, faster, and more professional code. This bundle is your passport to mastering the full spectrum of modern programming. Whether your goal is to build software from scratch, explore functional and object-oriented paradigms, or sharpen your craft with advanced techniques, you’ll find the resources here. Best of all, your purchase helps support charity while you expand your coding skills.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#javacodingproblems_secondedition"&gt;Java Coding Problems&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#learncprogramming"&gt;Learn C Programming&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pythonobject-orientedprogr