      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/594bf9cbcefe7ac769d4088899f7e55a3fa88128.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=27bf62e0202db22c8934764d30a3b09a"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ca1679f9906c4432119fa2d0285cf0137e16a15b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=0bd9e57745072e2106c4a329ba641e6e"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Fall in love with Shojo &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fill up on shojo manga this fall as Kodansha and Humble team-up to offer fans digital volumes of dramatic, heartwarming, and surprising sagas during the Fall In Love With Shojo Bundle! Just $30 gets you more than 80 digital volumes and over $900 worth of manga. This includes all volumes of modern classics like the love story steeped in trauma and healing, MARS, the magical girl adventure Shugo Chara!, the frenemies and lovers high school rom-com, Peach Girl, and more. Not only that but fans can catch up on nearly all volumes of the ongoing tender and wholesome school days romance, A Condition Called Love. It’s a perfect bundle for anyone who loves shojo or is curious to try some of Kodansha’s best. Explore amazing shojo manga from Kodansha and help support The BINC Foundation with your purchase!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#shugochara_vol1"&gt;Shugo Chara! Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#shugocharachan_vol1"&gt;Shugo Chara Chan! Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#peachgirl_vol1"&gt;Peach Girl Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mars_vol1"&gt;MARS Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sayiloveyou_vol1"&gt;Say I Love You Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#aconditioncalledlove_vol1"&gt;A Condition Called Love Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt10"&gt;Pay $10 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#shugochara_vol2-4"&gt;Shugo Chara! Vol.2-4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#shugocharachan_vol2"&gt;Shugo Chara Chan! Vol.2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#peachgirl_vol2-6"&gt;Peach Girl Vol.2-6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mars_vol2-5"&gt;MARS Vol.2-5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sayiloveyou_vol2-6"&gt;Say I Love You Vol.2-6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#aconditioncalledlove_vol2_6"&gt;A Condition Called Love Vol.2-6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#shugochara_vol5-8"&gt;Shugo Chara! Vol.5-8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#shugocharachan_vol3"&gt;Shugo Chara Chan! Vol.3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#peachgirl_vol7-12"&gt;Peach Girl Vol.7-12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mars_vol6-10"&gt;MARS Vol.6-10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sayiloveyou_vol7-12"&gt;Say I Love You Vol.7-12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#aconditioncalledlove_vol7-11"&gt;A Condition Called Love Vol.7-11&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#shugochara_vol9-12"&gt;Shugo Chara! Vol.9-12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#shugocharachan_vol4"&gt;Shugo Chara Chan! Vol.4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#peachgirl_vol13-18"&gt;Peach Girl Vol.13-18&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mars_vol11-15"&gt;MARS Vol.11-15&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sayiloveyou_vol13-18"&gt;Say I Love You Vol.13-18&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#aconditioncalledlove_vol12-16"&gt;A Condition Called Love Vol.12-16&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="shugochara_vol1"&gt;&lt;a id="shugochara_vol1" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/shugochara_vol1_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=feb9e362f5a1bd3b5ef4f2069fe4e70475f3751e90a03dc50ae99487567868ab"&gt;Shugo Chara! Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d78fee87770466a707f27c1356f6b9f865dcb96a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=11edf64aba497e4d1eb83d88542dce81"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Everybody at Seiyo Elementary thinks that stylish and super cool Amu has it all: But nobody knows the real Amu, a shy girl who wishes she had the courage to truly be herself. Changing Amu's life is going to take more than wishes and dreamsit's going to take a little magic! One morning, Amu finds a surprise in her bed: three strange little eggs. Each egg contains a Guardian Character, an angellike being who can give her the power to be someone new. With the help of her Guardian Characters, Amu is about to discover that her true self is even more amazing than she ever dreamed. This volume of Shugo Chara! includes special extras after the story!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="shugocharachan_vol1"&gt;&lt;a id="shugocharachan_vol1" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/shugocharachan_vol1_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=0157d1684d1b9b75b86f770ce604d4040cc1a8283ac98d4f2703be14cd73065d"&gt;Shugo Chara Chan! Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4db1931e1b2f19e6f97da623679c2f7badbd87f6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=806ee4520c12f5ed25c313c5050321ad"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Amu's beloved Guardians Characters finally nab the spotlight in this new Shugo Chara series! Ran, Miki, and Su explore holidays, exercise, bears, cooking, painting, and more character changes than you can count in these hilarious and lighthearted short stories, told in the vertical 4koma (4panel) comic strip format. Includes special extras after the story!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="peachgirl_vol1"&gt;&lt;a id="peachgirl_vol1" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/peachgirl_vol1_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=0eacbcbfd6ccaa155c4f38e6753e22353977bb0c3b8171eebca706f3bb6d458a"&gt;Peach Girl Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ab807c12873d8e3088bc0aac1da77369f5338bd9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6b3950e77a443e97ee2fa9c622d55219"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;It's not easy being beautiful. The envy, the jealousy, the vicious rumors spread by your best friend. That's life for young Momo. While everyone thinks that Momo is a wild party girl, the reality is that she is shy and honest. Can Momo confess her love to her classmate Toji, or will her best friend Sae steal him away. It's a bittersweet drama of growing up and fitting in that will charm girls everywhere.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mars_vol1"&gt;&lt;a id="mars_vol1" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/mars_vol1_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=01606a80811b0fac68f1ae44e778bbc57d2cf838f6722132a58b2f34c1dc9414"&gt;MARS Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9f56edbb9da0b6b509480d09dbc84176ee518455.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=030bc839ab58e69fbb056b4ce9e68baa"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Popular Rei and shy Kira are worlds apart, until one fateful day brings them together. Rei stumbles upon Kira in the harassing hands of her sleazy art teacher and saves the quiet girl from his clutches. And when the jock plants a kiss on a statue of Mars in the studio, Kira finds herself drawn in and even summons up the nerve to ask him to model for her!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sayiloveyou_vol1"&gt;&lt;a id="sayiloveyou_vol1" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/sayiloveyou_vol1_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=bf82b47bd04030da50dc0bd873c5cb6fd9de37f7981bd3750378b1b995fd4a1c"&gt;Say I Love You Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/aa71a68c6b06c84aab51d9843ef3120821269f5d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3127f1e0d0e4ff381f9977b523cfde57"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mei Tachibana has no friendsand she doesn't need them! Ever since her "friends" betrayed her in elementary school, she's sworn off friendship entirely. All it leads to is betrayal and heartbreak, and she's well enough on her own. But everything changes when she accidentally roundhouse kicks the most popular boy in school! However, Yamato Kurosawa isn't angry in the slightest in fact, he thinks his ordinary life could use an unusual girl like Mei! He won't take no for an answer, and soon Mei and Yamato embark on an unwanted friendship that will change both of them forever. PRAISE FOR THE ANIME "Surprises with its honesty, its sensitivity, its quality. Always it is smarter, more poetic, more touching, just plain better than you think it is going to be." Anime News Network&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="aconditioncalledlove_vol1"&gt;&lt;a id="aconditioncalledlove_vol1" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/aconditioncalledlove_vol1_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=308689d96d4cd2d4a5ad9012c077e0736038eb6ef56f400af078df609243e9cc"&gt;A Condition Called Love Vol.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/355af1435889233619d7e3113884da46ff951d1c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e3cf40b7bf6cf2b1f6a19c83102b5482"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hotaru is a 16-year-old high school first-year who has always been ambivalent about love, preferring instead to have a lively life with her family and friends. So when she sees her schoolmate, Hananoi-kun, sitting in the snow after a messy, public breakup, she thinks nothing of offering to share her umbrella. But when he asks her out in the middle of her classroom the next day, she can't help but feel that her life is about to change in a big way ...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt10"&gt;Pay $10 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="shugochara_vol2-4"&gt;&lt;a id="shugochara_vol2-4" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/shugochara_vol2-4_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=d96d93fa27e8298d7bc3004865647f0f3a9ea481f8ca850327d46a9d9e0ceef4"&gt;Shugo Chara! Vol.2-4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f971819413e368399aa4b62685b438a549e12432.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=64483bf5acc96cea83613eddec2c393c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Everybody at Seiyo Elementary thinks that stylish and supercool Amu has it all. But nobody knows the real Amu, a shy girl who wishes she had the courage to truly be herself. Changing Amu’s life is going to take more than wishes and dreams-it’s going to take a little magic! One morning, Amu finds a surprise in her bed: three strange little eggs. Each egg contains a Guardian Character, an angel-like being who can give her the power to be someone new. With the help of her Guardian Characters, Amu is about to discover that her true self is even more amazing than she ever dreamed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="shugocharachan_vol2"&gt;&lt;a id="shugocharachan_vol2" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/shugocharachan_vol2_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=1eb3c03f4db702e56f35e14fde6a0d539c3192319831d9ba9b69cc5a6c7d5992"&gt;Shugo Chara Chan! Vol.2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/756ccc1fb8982405659f5243bb536ecd6adaca5b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=271e2cabd5c3fd4fc4fb67a4ba9e120c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Amu's delightful guardians get their chance to shine in this brand new Shugo Chara Chan volume! Hilarious Christmas stories, adorable romances, and much more all told in the vertical 4koma (4panel) comic stript format. Includes special extras after the story!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="peachgirl_vol2-6"&gt;&lt;a id="peachgirl_vol2-6" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/peachgirl_vol2-6_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=cb2ead918806fbe5972e4ee1f3668b229e4d7c1ffd6715891481453af5555625"&gt;Peach Girl Vol.2-6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/74d3ea2e3a46696866fe171c7fc7d8124c775450.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=696c88202e7aa1703f57f7b10e7a07f9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The complete 18-volume run of Miwa Ueda’s ’90s shojo megahit &lt;em&gt;Peach Girl&lt;/em&gt; is back! Suntans and bleached hair were never quite so problematic, and high school drama was never quite so…. dramatic! This digital reissued edition combines the original English-language run of &lt;em&gt;Peach Girl&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Peach Girl: Change of Heart&lt;/em&gt;.  It’s not easy being beautiful. The envy, the jealousy, the vicious rumors spread by your best friend. That’s life for young Momo. While everyone thinks that Momo is a wild party girl, the reality is that she is shy and honest. Can Momo confess her love to her classmate Toji, or will her best friend Sae steal him away? It’s a bittersweet drama of growing up and fitting in that will charm girls everywhere.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mars_vol2-5"&gt;&lt;a id="mars_vol2-5" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/mars_vol2-5_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=1f1c1d85b209a1d417d3740d56f8933c7fde5902de07c1efc51b99ba02b240ee"&gt;MARS Vol.2-5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/057813bd41d3ff46c8df014ce1e81633068f7534.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f9aedc05bfa9b6942eb8cf947f0ca844"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you ready for some … drama? The all-time, long out-of-print shojo manga classic is back! With even more twists and turns then you probably remember, Fuyumi Soryo’s beautifully illustrated high-school psychodrama turned some young comics readers heads inside-out when it was first released, with hysterical plots revolving around the traumatic secret histories of its seemingly poised protagonists. Art class was never quite like this …&lt;/strong&gt;  Superpopular motorcycle racer Rei and shy, neurotic art student Kira are worlds apart … until one fateful day brings them together. Rei stumbles upon Kira in the harassing hands of her sleazy art teacher and saves the quiet girl from his clutches. And when the resident school pretty boy plants a kiss on a statue of Mars in the studio, Kira finds herself drawn in and even summons up the nerve to ask him to model for her!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sayiloveyou_vol2-6"&gt;&lt;a id="sayiloveyou_vol2-6" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/sayiloveyou_vol2-6_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=95d66d3f7897c35126aaa30ca3072ea2b8ac3b65a76a89746dc2309257daad05"&gt;Say I Love You Vol.2-6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7170a55bfb4b7500bbf80629a81cae5070570825.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=558eb2ad550f612774666d6bc6ccc306"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mei Tachibana has no friends—and she doesn’t need them! Ever since her “friends” betrayed her in elementary school, she’s sworn off friendship entirely. All it leads to is betrayal and heartbreak, and she’s well enough on her own. But everything changes when she accidentally roundhouse kicks the most popular boy in school! However, Yamato Kurosawa isn’t angry in the slightest—in fact, he thinks his ordinary life could use an unusual girl like Mei! He won’t take no for an answer, and soon Mei and Yamato embark on an unwanted friendship that will change both of them forever.  Praise for the anime: “Surprises with its honesty, its sensitivity, its quality. Always it is smarter, more poetic, more touching, just plain better than you think it is going to be.” —Anime News Network&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="aconditioncalledlove_vol2_6"&gt;&lt;a id="aconditioncalledlove_vol2_6" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/aconditioncalledlove_vol2_6_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=595d2f8f09d663389c9110ed5021e51fe0192f067eb3054da9073bdf4d16be2c"&gt;A Condition Called Love Vol.2-6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1427c986d785d29ddb7176b01774f545c88aa75a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5746c233baf700119556b90c2d7a4957"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hotaru doesn’t need a boyfriend. But an act of kindness to a classmate going through a breakup opens a door she never thought to step through, and everything begins to change… A sweet new shojo romance manga from the creator of &lt;em&gt;Wake Up, Sleeping Beauty&lt;/em&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="shugochara_vol5-8"&gt;&lt;a id="shugochara_vol5-8" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/shugochara_vol5-8_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=85597cf8c5c01ece5d319523e5d7042f88f8fcdceb5aefbdfd091f827228efc6"&gt;Shugo Chara! Vol.5-8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7507b0d73f8b872a14b9a36caa7e3d1477a78317.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=09bf7ee35ee1e4aaacd5968f4be4dc98"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Everybody at Seiyo Elementary thinks that stylish and supercool Amu has it all. But nobody knows the real Amu, a shy girl who wishes she had the courage to truly be herself. Changing Amu’s life is going to take more than wishes and dreams-it’s going to take a little magic! One morning, Amu finds a surprise in her bed: three strange little eggs. Each egg contains a Guardian Character, an angel-like being who can give her the power to be someone new. With the help of her Guardian Characters, Amu is about to discover that her true self is even more amazing than she ever dreamed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="shugocharachan_vol3"&gt;&lt;a id="shugocharachan_vol3" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/shugocharachan_vol3_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=b6f36b9e6d31b54fdd5f5bd1434c37bbbfb5431242464bb4f3d50a0a2c130959"&gt;Shugo Chara Chan! Vol.3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/06288668fbe9c40bd051f3b682101b9588ab921c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5789a93367dfd0d38147a1bb9b242d54"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Amu's pretty and cheerful guardians have many adorable experiences in this brand new volume of Shugo Chara Chan! Stories of singing ,fun, and adventure are all presented in this vertical 4koma (4panel) style. This "can't miss" volume also features bonus Shugo Chara stories drawn by some of your favorite manga artists! Includes special extras after the story!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="peachgirl_vol7-12"&gt;&lt;a id="peachgirl_vol7-12" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/peachgirl_vol7-12_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=4eab4b2757b0eeb997a2e61b4b6d72a1fd0e5f827241235d7c79365b23dc6637"&gt;Peach Girl Vol.7-12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/74803e671e540da85144fa3d4b328f1786c002b0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5acf467baa1041c4ef2e844e05e9fa93"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The complete 18-volume run of Miwa Ueda’s ’90s shojo megahit &lt;em&gt;Peach Girl&lt;/em&gt; is back! Suntans and bleached hair were never quite so problematic, and high school drama was never quite so…. dramatic! This digital reissued edition combines the original English-language run of &lt;em&gt;Peach Girl&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Peach Girl: Change of Heart&lt;/em&gt;.  It’s not easy being beautiful. The envy, the jealousy, the vicious rumors spread by your best friend. That’s life for young Momo. While everyone thinks that Momo is a wild party girl, the reality is that she is shy and honest. Can Momo confess her love to her classmate Toji, or will her best friend Sae steal him away? It’s a bittersweet drama of growing up and fitting in that will charm girls everywhere.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mars_vol6-10"&gt;&lt;a id="mars_vol6-10" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/mars_vol6-10_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=d9f5e0f0801f0e54896942adcda3814fb7734dd429747077b80c1f4c2626d0c4"&gt;MARS Vol.6-10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f84312ba59d26ed05f02e5b65be6631d15ea4079.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7818a401f4f68eff50ed9a68118811c5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you ready for some … drama? The all-time, long out-of-print shojo manga classic is back! With even more twists and turns then you probably remember, Fuyumi Soryo’s beautifully illustrated high-school psychodrama turned some young comics readers heads inside-out when it was first released, with hysterical plots revolving around the traumatic secret histories of its seemingly poised protagonists. Art class was never quite like this …&lt;/strong&gt;  Superpopular motorcycle racer Rei and shy, neurotic art student Kira are worlds apart … until one fateful day brings them together. Rei stumbles upon Kira in the harassing hands of her sleazy art teacher and saves the quiet girl from his clutches. And when the resident school pretty boy plants a kiss on a statue of Mars in the studio, Kira finds herself drawn in and even summons up the nerve to ask him to model for her!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sayiloveyou_vol7-12"&gt;&lt;a id="sayiloveyou_vol7-12" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/sayiloveyou_vol7-12_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=60baa129cf1deb7c6e0db592b0769796172e0a080a36dda849800137b829bfbf"&gt;Say I Love You Vol.7-12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f3a82bcdecba7fe1af9892b18a4f31fc17f25612.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=aa50ed5cbfd292bb0c1fdce62ab1bd2f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mei Tachibana has no friends—and she doesn’t need them! Ever since her “friends” betrayed her in elementary school, she’s sworn off friendship entirely. All it leads to is betrayal and heartbreak, and she’s well enough on her own. But everything changes when she accidentally roundhouse kicks the most popular boy in school! However, Yamato Kurosawa isn’t angry in the slightest—in fact, he thinks his ordinary life could use an unusual girl like Mei! He won’t take no for an answer, and soon Mei and Yamato embark on an unwanted friendship that will change both of them forever.  Praise for the anime: “Surprises with its honesty, its sensitivity, its quality. Always it is smarter, more poetic, more touching, just plain better than you think it is going to be.” —Anime News Network&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="aconditioncalledlove_vol7-11"&gt;&lt;a id="aconditioncalledlove_vol7-11" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/aconditioncalledlove_vol7-11_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=e3ce9f442773fd703db49a9053cdf07c7e17ccba1aee9143645769393f509b65"&gt;A Condition Called Love Vol.7-11&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/88233311942522b59c2bcfc2728778554675fb8d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e4ef6353fc2f899f9254b9afddeac4b1"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hotaru doesn’t need a boyfriend. But an act of kindness to a classmate going through a breakup opens a door she never thought to step through, and everything begins to change… A sweet new shojo romance manga from the creator of &lt;em&gt;Wake Up, Sleeping Beauty&lt;/em&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="shugochara_vol9-12"&gt;&lt;a id="shugochara_vol9-12" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/shugochara_vol9-12_preview.pdf?t=st=1758388312~exp=1758474712~hmac=bbfde95ced9ec14bbcd43484c01efbd7d38b5c2ed408a6dac4f731a7567f64b7"&gt;Shugo Chara! Vol.9-12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f06e830588b23e09cf0332f79fedc170746bbd06.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=49b915a7aa02a9f0589121f4678944bb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Everybody at Seiyo Elementary thinks that stylish and supercool Amu has it all. But nobody 