      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/eced774c193e995be610f4d77e9b1f1e56498a1d.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=54b5bf2c9779e9d14a8e732f330da16c"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/772fda3fe1889a8d1ee2d6b5ac4c57c2421fc14b.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=2fe42c708dc30585d1d52b7999ef5e96"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Live in the clouds with AWS &amp; Azure&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Become a 21st-century superstar with the latest Humble Tech Book Bundle: Cloud Infrastructure and DevOps Toolkit. Learn the intricacies of Amazon Web Services with industry-leading courses like &lt;em&gt;AWS for Solutions Architects&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;AWS Cloud Projects&lt;/em&gt;—master Microsoft Azure with professional-quality lessons like &lt;em&gt;Hands-On MLOps on Azure&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Azure for Developers&lt;/em&gt;. This comprehensive library includes lessons, practice tests, and resources perfect for novices and seasoned professionals alike—build strong foundations in cloud infrastructure and help support No Kid Hungry with your purchase.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cloudnativeanti-patterns"&gt;Cloud Native Anti-Patterns&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sustainableclouddevelopment"&gt;Sustainable Cloud Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ciandcddesignpatterns"&gt;CI/CD Design Patterns&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt12"&gt;Pay $12 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#kubernetesbible"&gt;The Kubernetes Bible&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#self-taughtcloudcomputingengineer"&gt;The Self-Taught Cloud Computing Engineer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ultimatedockercontainerbookthirdedition"&gt;The Ultimate Docker Container Book&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt18"&gt;Pay $18 or more to also