      <title>Capcom Retro Revival Pack</title>
      <author>Capcom Japan</author>
      <link>https://humblebundle.com//games/capcom-retro-revival-pack</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">421eb7f17f3afbb9d71471503cd9e3dd4c7bc937</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Sep 2025 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4ca60ce3b64651b3a8973269eaca1f3b51786e6c.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=c8ce6c65b07ec3afc108ccb0805c80c0"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/043cd772217dcd7c6bc26fcca7871c1e353d18de.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=2363742f6bdbf1d75d2b7c36a878fe22"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Retro vibes from Capcom&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore 30+ iconic titles from years past and the latest retro-inspired releases with the all-new Capcom Retro Revival Bundle! Play classic throwbacks like &lt;em&gt;Super Street Fighter II Turbo&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Bionic Commando&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Strider&lt;/em&gt;, and &lt;em&gt;Section Z&lt;/em&gt;—plus &lt;em&gt;Ghosts ’n Goblins Resurrection&lt;/em&gt;, a reimagining of the notoriously difficult 1985 side-scroller. You can also dive into 2013’s &lt;em&gt;Dungeons &amp; Dragons: Chronicles of Mystara&lt;/em&gt;—a compelling blend of old-school arcade mechanics and rich D&amp;D lore. Pay what you want for timeless Capcom games and help support Children’s Miracle Network Hospitals with your purchase.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a style="color:#EF9741"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Games from the CAPCOM Arcade Stadium Complete Pack are collected into one key.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $20 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ghostsngoblinsresurrection"&gt;Ghosts N' Goblins Resurrection&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#dnd_chroniclesofmystara"&gt;Dungeons &amp; Dragons: Chronicles of Mystara&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#strider"&gt;Strider&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#capcomarcadestadiumcompletepack"&gt;Capcom Arcade Stadium Complete Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#capcomarcadestadiumsuperstreetfighteriiturbo"&gt;Super Street Fighter II Turbo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#capcomarcade2ndstadium_hyperstreetfighterii_