lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 184 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 65&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 221&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.5, 5.6+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="parkwayhome"&gt;&lt;a id="parkwayhome"&gt;Parkway Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/02bc73cbf70a1abbdd1a7f22425369557d19ccdd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=42979feaf6bd3857fe4e61d7f7f1231b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Parkway Home – Modern Family House with Stylish Interior Environment with 124 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased and high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;DISCLAIMER:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Nanite/Lumen Enabled&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;HDRI plugin Enabled&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This product supports Lumen for Unreal Engine 5.0.3&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;124 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed assets, 2048 for mid-sized assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets are used as standard. Various sizes are used for unique assets where needed, with the smallest resolution being 1x1.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 126 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 229&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 297&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stylizedcastleenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="stylizedcastleenvironment"&gt;Stylized Castle Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/811509f78c06ec0818faf79bb7191744904eacb1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a2d9abd166cd980056da6582ea42e58a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A Stylized Castle Environment with 65 Assets. Many different types of Assets help you create or polish your Environments. All Assets are made with unique concepts, and a Showcased Example level is also included in the Project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Gameready / Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 65&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 70&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 87&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 4K, 2K, 1K:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="windmill"&gt;&lt;a id="windmill"&gt;Windmill&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4d253e85e933362b97fff57352724a87d201699f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=600f2dca800466e698dc7425adafd713"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This environment pack features 5 uniquely crafted meshes, including all showcased assets in high quality. Built with performance in mind, it's fully optimized for game-ready projects and virtual production.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;5 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt