ws&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build Platforms: Window/Mac/PS4/Xbox&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="romanstatuespackvol1"&gt;&lt;a id="romanstatuespackvol1"&gt;Roman Statues Pack Vol 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8f6042d3e972fb332693c30311ea39529c4640bd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0b0e089e5d4d04e71cdedbcea605435d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;11 Realistic High-Quality Roman Statues&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This package provides eleven high-quality and well-optimized statues to populate your game environments or virtual production levels.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please create a ticket for all your promotional requests, technical support needs, suggestions, and refund requests.Number of Unique Meshes: 14&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials: 1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Material Instances: 5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 21&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 1K to 2K&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac: No&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;5.0 – 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cyberpunkbenches"&gt;&lt;a id="cyberpunkbenches"&gt;Cyberpunk Benches&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1d761eead116d922c66329b811ff8bdb8891f52e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9551f3cec737122caac35158e00f9a43"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cyberpunk Benches with 10 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased assets and high-quality assets. It has a good level of detail and is optimized for Gameready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to populate your game environments or any Virtual Production levels, here is the pack you can use to get high-quality visuals and well-optimized assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;105 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Automatically Generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 10 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 22&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 50&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 4.26 , 4.27+ , 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cyberpunkassaultrifles"&gt;&lt;a id="cyberpunkassaultrifles"&gt;Cyberpunk Assault Rifles&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5570a23bb8843d2c6153b4d4adcdb9988f13a673.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f2a4a4a6aad039f4bed3ec89d3355100"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cyberpunk Assault Rifles with 82 Unique Meshes. This includes all showcased assets, which are high-quality assets with a good level of detail and optimized for Game-Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;** IMPORTANT NOTE: The asset pack has 82 Unique Meshes. 13 of them are complete weapons, and 69 are smaller parts of the guns. For instance, one of the complete weapons has a combined static mesh, and the handgrip, silencer, and sights have static meshes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to populate your game environments or any Virtual Production levels, here is the pack you can use to get high-quality visuals and well-optimized assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;82 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;128&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Automatically Generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 57 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 77&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 213&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 4.26 , 4.27+ , 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="militaryhelicopter_riggedandbpcontrollablewandskins"&gt;&lt;a id="militaryhelicopter_riggedandbpcontrollablewandskins"&gt;Military Helicopter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/250869694677ed2e9564863bb3382c6d4a987363.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f3ee8a09c3aed3ab48051303be693891"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project includes everything pictured, including all assets, maps, and materials created in the Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic AAA quality visuals, style, and budget.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Art was created in collaboration with Leartes and Dekogon Studios.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Animation and Blueprint setup by Leartes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Art by Dekogon Studios.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pitch can be controlled by W key and S key&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Steer can be controlled by A key and D key&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Throttle can be controlled with E and Q key&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Camera Rotation can be controlled by Mouse&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;F and G Key - Open/Close Doors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Helicopter Materials are changeable in Detail Panel&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Setup for easy drop and play&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Custom sounds&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master Material to control features&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Multiple Design Skins&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes static mesh version in addition to skeletal mesh and blueprint&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;4K Texture Sets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master material setup that control the majority of all props and models&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Channel packed Roughness | Metalness | Ambient Occlusion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for games&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Free of all legal issues as all branding and labels are custom made by our studio&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models from all sides&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes test dynamic lighting scene&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="classicracecar"&gt;&lt;a id="classicracecar"&gt;Classic Race Car&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/04773865440261fcbcbdd28655151be5f73561a6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9bc40827bb73b4d0d9067c0a14499872"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Classic Race Car Driveable / Animated / Realistic / Fully Customizable with separate Parts / Blueprints / Material Instances. There are Roughness / Metallic / Color parameters in material instances so you can arrange materials easily; the Vehicle will be in one blueprint and also six separate meshes, so you will be able to use them as you wish to create a prop for your Levels / Games and Automotive presentations / ArchViz.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can Activate ( Open / Close ) Car doors with four buttons ( one button for each, Q E R F ) via keyboard, and you can change the camera view while driving the Car.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rigged , Driveable , Playable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Radio System Added&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All Sounds included.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Good to use in Automotive Industry / ArchViz / Games&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Dirt / Edge Wears&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Lights&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy switch between material values ( roughness / metallic / color )&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;One button Animating Car's Doors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully Customizable / Material Variations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;4096 / 2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, automatically generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 8&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 37&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26 , 4.27+ , 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="fps4kcustommodernshotguns_vol2unrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="fps4kcustommodernshotguns_vol2unrealengine"&gt;FPS 4K Custom Modern Shotguns - VOL.2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/857ea5a7cdd2582bf4a7b22c207d870cb53de63d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4c7dbed510ab2329f6edcf45263dc1bf"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project includes everything pictured, including all assets, maps, and materials created in the Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic AAA quality visuals, style, and budget.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;(Set of 5) 4K Textured, Highly detailed custom designed modern first person shooter quality Shotguns&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes full gun assembled and individual gun parts - 53 Meshes total&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pre Assembled into Blueprint setup&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High quality and fidelity texture sets - 4k Textures&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Uses only 1 material for single draw call per gun + Additional Glass Material for sights see through&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master material setup that control the all the guns with instances for ease of changes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Channel packed Roughness | Metalness | Ambient Occlusion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic Post Process and Look Up Table&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for games for FPS view!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Free of all legal issues as all branding and labels are custom made by our studio&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes test dynamic lighting scene&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pivots placed for ease of animation and usage&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096 [18]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024 [3]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;512 [1]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;256 [1]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;128 [3]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Scaled to Epic skeleton: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, automatically generated and per-poly mix based on complexity of asset&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vertex Count:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Twins (11559 Tris)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Kicking Bull (7218 Tris)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CP5 (20716 Tris)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;RAM (15707 Tris)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;SUM12 (8049 Tris)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Base LOD only&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 53&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 10&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 26&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: Windows&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build Platforms: Window/Mac/PS4/Xbox&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="suv04driveableandanimatedandrealisticunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="suv04driveableandanimatedandrealisticunrealengine"&gt;SUV 04 Driveable / Animated&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/07fabe3b627bd542bb195c98dcc16ce14b5c0afd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8b286b808c4bf177cecd49202260ad85"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;SUV Driveable / Animated / Realistic / Fully Customizable with separate Parts / Blueprints / Material Instances. Material instances have Roughness / Metallic / Color parameters so that you can arrange materials easily. The Vehicle will be in one blueprint and eight separate meshes, so you can use them to create props for your Levels / Games and Automotive presentations / ArchViz.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can Activate ( Open / Close ) Car doors with four buttons ( one button for each, Q E R F ) via keyboard, and you can change the camera view while driving the Car.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Video: https://youtu.be/ydGc7HynhoQ&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note: This car is also included in our SUV Bundle&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Documentation about how to use the car here&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;SC_Doors sound plays with blueprint when pressing F, E, Q, R&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rigged , Driveable , Playable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Good to use in Automotive Industry / ArchViz / Games&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Dirt / Edge Wears&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Lights&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy switch between material values ( roughness / metallic / color )&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;One button Animating Car's Doors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully Customizable / Material Variations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;4096 / 2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, automatically generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 8&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 4&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 8&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 4.19 , 4.20 , 4.21 , 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26+, 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxwarzone"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxwarzone"&gt;SFX Warzone&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/31586966564c4ae17df78e7f9fb6608b896c17d5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4a620b9abcfd70dc26f12224bb5d1720"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;WW2 Warzone-themed Sound pack .&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The product works with UE.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The SFX packs Contains :&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;1 Ambience Sound Loop&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;5 Bombing Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;6 Chest opening Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;4 Building destruction Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;20 Glass Destruction Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;10 Fire Destruction Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;4 StickGranade Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;4 Rifle Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;8 PaperFluttering Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;12 Machine Gun Fire and Tail Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;4 Cannonball Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2 Lamp Open/Close Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1 Phone Ringing Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;11 Piano Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;3 Wall Clock Sound&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Total 95 Audio file.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="warzonevfxpackunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="warzonevfxpackunrealengine"&gt;VFX Warzone (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e25ca8e69f8ef3f016c0d5126baa1f6a1d83665d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f0dd5569731b9e124db404a558b98d74"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Warzone-themed 6 different visual effects. Including all showcased assets, and high-quality Visual Effects With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to populate your game environments or any kind of Virtual Production levels here is the pack that you get and use to get high-quality visuals and well-optimized assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vfxexplosionunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="vfxexplosionunrealengine"&gt;VFX Explosion (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6752e7b51f23ae6dd3bb53aaa96eeb1f4f3411e5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=502f5665678a96f00ba139089d5e60eb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Game-ready custom Explosions for your Unreal Engine Games&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unreal Engine Version: 5.0&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cosmos1monthsubscription"&gt;&lt;a id="cosmos1monthsubscription" href="https://youtu.be/-j_eFTcEuLY"&gt;Cosmos 1 month subscription&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https:/