      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3b415ed7a2ce744796764affec9d7fb2a3aa4b3c.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=203c022dd653eb291327d35565c821b6"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3c6b472fc1956c21bc1863ce1de9182c3aa83548.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=ad1bf72713dc2db84e7fac85f8bee73c"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Learn Unity—bring your games to life &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get serious about game creation and take your passion to the next level with our latest bundle! Learn essential game development skills for one of today’s most popular platforms—Unity. The Unity Engine is approachable, powerful, and perfect for creators of all skill levels. Dive into top-rated courses like &lt;em&gt;Complete Unity 2D C# Developer Course&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Unity Real Time Strategy Course&lt;/em&gt;, and &lt;em&gt;Unity Turn Based Strategy Course&lt;/em&gt;. Pay what you want for a bundle that can transform your career—and help support Charity: Water with your purchase.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unitygamefeelcourse"&gt;Unity Game Feel Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#fromblendertounitycourse"&gt;From Blender to Unity Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unityproceduralgenerationcourse"&gt;Unity Procedural Generation Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unitycutscenes_mastercinematicsanimationandtrailerscourse"&gt;Unity Cutscenes: Master Cinematics, Animation and Trailers Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unityrealtimestrategycourse"&gt;Unity Real Time Strategy Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#completeunity2dcdevelopercourseupdatedtounity6"&gt;Complete Unity 2D C# Developer Course (in Unity 6)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#completeunity3dcdevelopercourse"&gt;Complete Unity 3D C# Developer Course (in Unity 6)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unitymultiplayercodingandnetworkingngo"&gt;Unity Multiplayer Coding &amp; Networking NGO Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unityturnbasedstrategycourse"&gt;Unity Turn Based Strategy Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unityshadergraphcourse"&gt;Unity Shader Graph Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unity2drpg_completecombatsystemcourse"&gt;Unity 2D RPG: Complete Combat System Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#programmingdesignpatternsforunitycourse"&gt;Programming Design Patterns For Unity Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sci-fimodularstarshipsandcarrierskit"&gt;Sci-Fi Modular Starships &amp; Carriers Kit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#elvenvillagemusicpack"&gt;Elven Music Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="unitygamefeelcourse"&gt;&lt;a id="unitygamefeelcourse" href="https://youtu.be/zloOv5LS4xY"&gt;Unity Game Feel Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ever feel that your game just doesn’t feel quite right?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to fix that by implementing a bunch of fun systems, mechanics and effects to enhance the way your game feels from a player perspective!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Building upon solid C# and Unity foundations, it’s time for you to level up.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Increase your C# understanding, learning how to implement things like a struct, centralized input, interfaces, and several game design patterns.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;And expand on your Unity knowledge by learning screen shake, post-processing effects, 2D lighting, particle effects, tilemap prefabs, masking, Unity events, and much more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Plus, you’ll even build an expandable Audio Manager system that can be used in other mid-sized scalable projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You’ll start with a 2D side scroller shooter base template and expand on it to get things feeling the way they should.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Make a game that “feels” fun to play with a clean and snappy player controller, a gun that’s fun to shoot, audio and screen visuals to give your player feedback, as well as animations to bring everything together.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Grab the bundle today and get your game feeling just right!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="fromblendertounitycourse"&gt;&lt;a id="fromblendertounitycourse" href="https://youtu.be/QQQmXENToqU"&gt;From Blender to Unity Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Got cool models in Blender but Unity keeps throwing a wobbly when you import them?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course teaches the exact workflow to get your assets from Blender into Unity, clean, crisp and game-ready.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You’ll bake textures, rig characters with Rigify and export animations that actually work in-engine.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn to set up LODs, build control rigs and pick the right file formats so nothing breaks on import.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect for artists and devs who want to stop relying on pre-made stuff and start building their own pipeline.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pick up the bundle now and finally make Unity play nice with your Blender creations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="unityproceduralgenerationcourse"&gt;&lt;a id="unityproceduralgenerationcourse" href="https://youtu.be/BlXCtnXmxjM"&gt;Unity Procedural Generation Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Want to build infinite game levels that stay fresh every time?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn to code your own procedural dungeons with hallways, rooms and just the right amount of chaos.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Turn 2D layouts into full 3D scenes with Marching Squares and power it all with Scriptable Objects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add runtime NavMesh so players and enemies can actually get around without faceplanting into walls.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Spawn loot, baddies and decorations using rules that keep things interesting (and not super samey).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You’ll level up your C# skills too, with advanced techniques that make your code lean and mean.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect for devs who know their way around Unity and want to create replayable worlds.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dive into the bundle and start generating awesome levels on the fly now!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unitycutscenes_mastercinematicsanimationandtrailerscourse"&gt;&lt;a id="unitycutscenes_mastercinematicsanimationandtrailerscourse" href="https://youtu.be/n04jlBK729Q"&gt;Unity Cutscenes: Master Cinematics, Animation and Trailers Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ready to make cinematic moments that’ll keep players hooked? This course is your power-up for mastering Unity’s Cinemachine, Timeline, and Animation tools. We’re diving into cut-scenes and epic trailers that'll give your game unforgettable flair - no prior cut-scene experience needed!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jump in with humanoid animations and Unity’s Timeline, where you'll animate characters and cameras for smooth, pro-level sequences. Learn to rig dynamic camera setups with Cinemachine to capture every action-packed moment, and add AAA polish with features like dolly and clear shot cameras.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Finish strong with a cinematic trailer challenge to push your skills to new levels. Ready to level up? Let’s get cinematic!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="unityrealtimestrategycourse"&gt;&lt;a id="unityrealtimestrategycourse" href="https://youtu.be/M4enqMidRpU"&gt;Unity Real Time Strategy Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ever wanted to build your own RTS but didn’t know where to start?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course teaches you how to create the full package, units, buildings, fog of war, upgrades and more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You’ll wrangle behaviour trees for smarter AI, set up scalable systems and ditch the spaghetti code for clean, config-driven goodness.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Use ScriptableObjects and event buses to keep your game tidy (and future you sane).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add new units and upgrades straight from the editor - no more hard-coded chaos.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you know your way around Unity and C#, this is your chance to level up and go full commander mode.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pick up the bundle and start building the RTS game you’ve always wanted to play.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="completeunity2dcdevelopercourseupdatedtounity6"&gt;&lt;a id="completeunity2dcdevelopercourseupdatedtounity6" href="https://youtu.be/u7hn8KGCnBE"&gt;Complete Unity 2D C# Developer Course (in Unity 6)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Want to make 2D games but don’t know where to start? This best-selling course takes you from total beginner to confident Unity dev - no experience needed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You’ll build 4 awesome games while learning clean C# code, tilemaps, sprite shapes and everything Unity’s 2D toolkit has to offer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;From platformers to shooters, each project helps you level up your skills and confidence.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You'll get hands-on experience, real support and lifetime access to keep learning at your own pace.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're an artist, aspiring dev or just love games, this course is your perfect starting point.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dive into the bundle and bring your first (or next!) 2D game to life with Unity 6.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="completeunity3dcdevelopercourse"&gt;&lt;a id="completeunity3dcdevelopercourse" href="https://youtu.be/5dwb0G0YxI4"&gt;Complete Unity 3D C# Developer Course (in Unity 6)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ready to level up your game dev skills? Dive into our Unity 6 course and learn from the team that’s taught over a million students to code and build games. Unity is a powerful 3D engine, but it can feel like a boss fight for beginners. Don’t worry—we’ve got your back with step-by-step projects that make coding fun and easy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You’ll create five games, each teaching you core skills. Dodge obstacles, blast aliens, and master everything from C# basics to advanced stuff like procedural generation and AI. Jump into projects like "Obstacle Dodge," "Rocket Boost," and "Sharp Shooter," where you’ll learn player controls, physics, AI, and more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With clear guidance, lifetime access, and all files included, we make sure you’re set up for success. No coding experience? No problem—start from scratch and go pro in no time.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;What are you waiting for? Dive into Unity 6 and start crafting your dream games!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unitymultiplayercodingandnetworkingngo"&gt;&lt;a id="unitymultiplayercodingandnetworkingngo" href="https://youtu.be/JRuVFdI_sg4"&gt;Unity Multiplayer Coding &amp; Networking NGO Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ready to make your own large scale game that supports dozens of players?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn to build an online game using the latest and greatest framework from Unity, which makes it easy to build multiplayer games (and saves time!)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;From building the core gameplay, to taking your game online, to making it deployable as a dedicated server and learning to integrate matchmaking. You'll do it all! Unity is making the process easier than ever with its new Netcode For GameObjects (NGO) framework.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You’ll make a multiplayer top-down shooter, you can play with dozens of people over the internet. And learn how to deploy a dedicated server with matchmaking!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re making a .io style game (like slither.io and agar.io), that can accommodate dozens of players. Through that process you’ll build the skills to make your own competitive or cooperative multiplayer game in any genre that interests you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jump in and start creating your own multiplayer game now. You’ll be playing it with your friends in no time!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unityturnbasedstrategycourse"&gt;&lt;a id="unityturnbasedstrategycourse" href="https://youtu.be/OKU7Px5bBn4"&gt;Unity Turn Based Strategy Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Are you looking to level up your game development skills and take your projects to the next level?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Want to make your own turn-based strategy game, similar to XCOM or Final Fantasy Tactics?*&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is the course for you!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this course, you’ll take your skills from beginner to advanced, learn to manage and organise a complex project. You’ll create a custom Grid System and learn advanced Programming concepts, such as; C# generics, C# events, custom structs, enemy AI, A* Pathfinding and much more!!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;* Even if you’re not interested in turn-based strategy games, these skills are super transferable to other types of games.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unityshadergraphcourse"&gt;&lt;a id="unityshadergraphcourse" href="https://youtu.be/sgH4aDEaQkY"&gt;Unity Shader Graph Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the magic of Unity Shader Graph and create visuals that’ll make your players say “Wow!” Dive into our course and master this powerful tool to craft stunning, dynamic effects for your games—no art degree needed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this course, you’ll learn to design immersive materials, jaw-dropping lighting, and gameplay-enhancing effects with Shader Graph. From procedural textures that add rich detail to custom lighting that brings your scenes to life, you’ll level up your visual storytelling skills and create effects that truly pop.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect for both beginners and pros, this hands-on, project-based course guides you through each step with high-quality tutorials and practical exercises. Let’s make your games unforgettable—grab this bundle and get ready to wow!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unity2drpg_completecombatsystemcourse"&gt;&lt;a id="unity2drpg_completecombatsystemcourse" href="https://youtu.be/OSXieQQrjJg"&gt;Unity 2D RPG: Complete Combat System Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ready to create your own classic 2D top-down RPG game in Unity?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Building an RPG is an amazing way to level-up your game development skills, so grab your magic staff, watch out for projectile grapes and start improving your game development right now! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Role Playing Games can be complex to create, with many interacting gameplay systems. We’ve made it easy for you, this course teaches you step-by-step how to make the foundations of any good RPG - from scratch!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; You'll learn 2D top-down movement, combining C# and animator components, a combat system with multiple weapons, scene management &amp;amp; scene persistence, tilemap, rule tiles, animated tiles, scene workflow and much more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="programmingdesignpatternsforunitycourse"&gt;&lt;a id="programmingdesignpatternsforunitycourse" href="https://youtu.be/2IKMw6b8YaI"&gt;Programming Design Patterns For Unity Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Want to take your coding to the next level? Learning how to apply programming best practices to your Unity projects will help!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Do you ever wonder why your code has so many bugs or find yourself perplexed by code you wrote months ago?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Maybe you've heard of Programming Patterns but don't understand when to use them, or you want to know how to actually implement these Patterns in Unity?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course covers fundamental programming best practices (including how to write clean, maintainable code), what problems to solve with Programming Patterns, how to write common Patterns in Unity and how Programming Patterns implement best practices.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You'll need a strong understanding of basic C# programming (classes, methods, ifs, loops) and some familiarity with more advanced concepts (inheritance, interfaces, events). And don’t worry if you don’t know this stuff at the moment, we cover all of these topics in the other courses in this bundle.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you’re ready to code better, this is the course for you!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sci-fimodularstarshipsandcarrierskit"&gt;&lt;a id="sci-fimodularstarshipsandcarrierskit" href="https://youtu.be/UvxoUd_tDzk"&gt;Sci-Fi Modular Starships &amp; Carriers Kit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bring your galactic fleet to life with the &lt;strong&gt;Sci-Fi - Modular Starships &amp;amp; Carriers Kit&lt;/strong&gt;, a versatile collection of 21 unique spaceships and hundreds of modular pieces. From nimble fighters to colossal motherships, each craft is meticulously designed to fill essential roles in your sci-fi world. Whether you're building an interstellar defense fleet, a cargo convoy, or a group of daring space explorers, these detailed ships are ready to populate your universe with depth and realism.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="elvenvillagemusicpack"&gt;&lt;a id="elvenvillagemusicpack" href="https://youtu.be/u7Kt3rDRv6A"&gt;Elven Music Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9c85256232f67ee1955ed4ae633e33adf0d21a45.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0b808d2dec456f4663e95a19007ab26d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Need music that makes your game feel like it was forged in the heart of a fantasy realm?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This Elven Village pack brings 14 beautifully crafted tracks to set the mood, from lively village squares to tranquil forest glades.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Designed by composer Jorge Velasco, each piece is ready to drop into your game and transport players straight to Elven lands.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect for fantasy games, RPGs, or any project that needs a touch of magic.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're scoring temples, tundras, or twinkling rivers - this pack's got you covered.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pick up the bundle and give your game a soundtrack worthy of legends.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
