ong&gt;&lt;!-- Comments are visible in the HTML source only --&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="messanger_ancientmountainunityassetstorekey"&gt;&lt;a id="messanger_ancientmountainunityassetstorekey" href="https://youtu.be/NNKqC36ziS4"&gt;The Messanger: Ancient Mountain (Unity Asset Store Key)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Check It Out On The Unity Asset Store &lt;a href="https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/3d/environments/fantasy/mountain-ancient-mountain-environment-276791"&gt;Here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*Unity asset store key is provided!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Background&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;"The messenger is a spiritual being acting as a messenger between the gods and the settlers that inhabit these ancient lands"&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt; &lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage - A large foliage library that can be used across all your projects!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Massive - 66 Unique meshes that enable the creation of massive ancient themed cities and towns!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Visual FX - Use a vast library of rich visual effects to instantly enhance any scene you might be working on! Including Waterfall fx, Leaf effects and most importantly a highly versatile local volumetric fog to be used across all of your scenes.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
