      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/01cf9d8f21b0fd0b2cd71434e22c21f74b2fc1bd.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=612d5d456dc567ba752f6bfc41aa3dd0"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/825227e5bed555c7ce8cdb92edb98f10c1bb4478.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=d4cc535752006f0724ff8b9a18132ece"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Mix it up with Blender assets&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add open-source 3D creation skills to your toolkit with our latest Software Bundle: Blender 3D Modeling Courses! Whether you’re a beginner or a seasoned pro, get comprehensive, professional-quality training covering every aspect of Blender in one complete library.  Learn from standout sessions from Eldamar Studio like &lt;em&gt;Learn Geometry Nodes Animation in Blender&lt;/em&gt;, the &lt;em&gt;Creating a Modern House In Blender Course&lt;/em&gt;, the &lt;em&gt;Procedural Materials In Blender Course&lt;/em&gt;, and more. Pay what you want for priceless 3D modeling skills—and help support Save the Children with your purchase!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#blenderbasicsforbeginnerscourse"&gt;Blender Basics For Beginners Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#creatinglowpolycyberpunksceneswithblender"&gt;Creating Low Poly Cyberpunk Scenes with Blender&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#proceduralmaterialsinblendercourse"&gt;Procedural Materials In Blender Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#lowpolyenvironmentscenecourse"&gt;Low Poly Environment Scene Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#learngeometrynodesanimationinblender"&gt;Learn Geometry Nodes Animation in Blender&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#creatingamodernhouseinblendercourse"&gt;Creating a Modern House In Blender Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&