      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5f4c6d1207ce2dedddaf4e081d343a63c22ed592.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=5ca39405abef518fc2526e6a14db59d4"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9a9dc3509c23f6e3a623a7f5edba6fecf4ac4af5.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=8b89b005db7e167f3beaabf6dd1e7439"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Learn endlessly with Skillademia&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add new skills to your creative toolbelt with our latest Software Bundle with awesome digital art and illustration courses from the experts at Skillademia. Learn how to draw and design original people, animals, and more like a pro with the &lt;em&gt;Character Design Course: Master Character Digital Illustration&lt;/em&gt; course, master the principles of drawing and sketching in Procreate with the &lt;em&gt;Procreate Course: Master Digital Illustration&lt;/em&gt; course, and more. Pay what you want and help support Make-A-Wish with your purchase!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#procreate"&gt;Procreate Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#adobeillustrator"&gt;Adobe Illustrator Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt10"&gt;Pay $10 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#canva"&gt;Canva Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#clipstudiopaint"&gt;Clip Studio Paint Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#characterdesign"&gt;Character Design Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pixelart"&gt;Pixel Art Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#comicbookcreation"&gt;Comic Book Creation Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="procreate"&gt;&lt;a id="procreate" href="https://youtu.be/8Yendya7Qts"&gt;Procreate Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock your digital art potential with our comprehensive Procreate course. Designed for aspiring artists, this course takes you from mastering the basics of Procreate’s intuitive interface to advanced techniques in illustration, sketching, and digital painting. Learn how to harness Procreate’s powerful brushes, layers, and effects to create stunning artwork. With step-by-step projects, you'll develop skills in color theory, composition, and creative workflow. You will be able to produce professional-level digital illustrations. Ideal for hobbyists and those seeking to build a career in digital art, this course provides the tools and techniques to bring your creative visions to life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="adobeillustrator"&gt;&lt;a id="adobeillustrator" href="https://youtu.be/1ANzuiDViJ0"&gt;Adobe Illustrator Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Become proficient in Adobe Illustrator, the industry-standard for vector graphics, with this in-depth course. You’ll start with the basics - navigating the interface, drawing shapes, and understanding paths, and progress to advanced techniques such as custom brushes, typography, and complex logo design. Through hands‑on projects, you’ll learn to create scalable artwork perfect for branding, marketing, and digital media. This course equips you with the essential skills to produce professional-grade illustrations and graphics, making it an ideal choice for beginners and aspiring design professionals looking to build a strong visual portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt10"&gt;Pay $10 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="canva"&gt;&lt;a id="canva" href="https://youtu.be/g8Oj3LHMkQo"&gt;Canva Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master the full potential of Canva and elevate your design skills with this comprehensive course. Dive into the fundamentals of graphic design and learn how to create eye-catching visuals, social media posts, marketing materials, and presentations using Canva’s intuitive drag‑and‑drop interface. The course covers color theory, typography, layout design, and branding essentials, along with practical tips for creating custom templates and streamlined workflows. Perfect for entrepreneurs, marketers, and aspiring designers, you’ll finish the course with a versatile toolkit to produce professional designs quickly and efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="clipstudiopaint"&gt;&lt;a id="clipstudiopaint" href="https://youtu.be/aGJ3G-_oxJc"&gt;Clip Studio Paint Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master the dynamic world of digital illustration with Clip Studio Paint in this extensive course. Learn how to harness the powerful features of Clip Studio Paint - from advanced brush settings and layer management to vector tools and animation techniques. The course is designed to help you create detailed illustrations, comics, and animations by exploring everything from sketching fundamentals and inking to coloring and effects. With step‑by‑step projects and practical exercises, you’ll gain the skills to refine your artistic style and produce professional-quality digital artwork, whether for personal passion or commercial projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="characterdesign"&gt;&lt;a id="characterdesign" href="https://youtu.be/gApLRFTDQBI"&gt;Character Design Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unleash your creativity with this all‑encompassing character design course. Discover the process of transforming ideas into compelling visual characters by learning core principles such as anatomy, proportion, and silhouette. The course covers concept development, sketching, and refining techniques that bring your characters to life, along with guidance on exploring different styles and personalities. Through practical projects and expert insights, you’ll build a robust portfolio that showcases your ability to craft unique, memorable characters for animation, gaming, or comics. Ideal for aspiring illustrators and storytellers eager to create impactful designs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pixelart"&gt;&lt;a id="pixelart" href="https://youtu.be/hULrmcb24IE"&gt;Pixel Art Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into the nostalgic and vibrant world of pixel art with this comprehensive course. Learn the fundamentals of creating detailed pixel-based images and animations using techniques such as dithering, color palette management, and anti-aliasing. The curriculum guides you through crafting everything from characters and backgrounds to game assets, blending traditional retro aesthetics with modern design practices. With engaging, project‑based lessons, you’ll develop the technical precision and artistic creativity needed to produce striking pixel art, ideal for game design, digital illustration, and creative experimentation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="comicbookcreation"&gt;&lt;a id="comicbookcreation" href="https://youtu.be/X0Z8nSyP7FM"&gt;Comic Book Creation Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Transform your storytelling through the art of comic book creation with this in-depth course. Learn to plan, design, and execute your own comic book by mastering narrative structure, panel layout, pacing, and visual storytelling. The curriculum covers drawing techniques, inking, coloring, and lettering, as well as digital tools that streamline comic production. With hands‑on projects and step‑by‑step guidance, you’ll develop the skills to create engaging characters and dynamic storylines, turning your creative ideas into a polished comic book ready for publication or digital distribution. Perfect for budding comic artists and storytellers alike.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
